snippet.title: RotMG Exalt Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
July 22, 2020: Realm of the Mad God Exalt will officially be out!
New game engine, new class, new final boss (Oryx 3) and much, much more!
Be prepared for some bullets! They don't call it bullet HELL for nothing...
